'''保加利亚号'''（{{lang-ru|Булгария|Bulgariya}}）又稱'''布尔加号'''<ref>{{cite news |title=俄罗斯发生沉船事故 |url=http://news.cntv.cn/special/Rchenchuan/shouye/index.shtml |accessdate=2021-06-05 |archive-date=2021-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605030658/http://news.cntv.cn/special/Rchenchuan/shouye/index.shtml }}</ref>，是一艘785/OL800级（斯洛伐克）<ref name="specs">{{cite web | url=http://top.rbc.ru/society/10/07/2011/604834.shtml | title=Теплоход проекта 785 "Булгария". Справка | publisher=RBC.ru | accessdate=11 July 2011 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110712230135/http://top.rbc.ru/society/10/07/2011/604834.shtml | archivedate=2011-07-12 | language=ru | dead-url=yes }}</ref>苏联/俄罗斯内河[[邮轮|邮轮]]，该船在伏尔加河-[[顿河|顿河]]流域航行。2011年7月10日，保加利亚号在[[伏尔加河|伏尔加河]]的[[古比雪夫水库|古比雪夫水库]]靠近[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[鞑靼斯坦|鞑靼斯坦]][[卡姆斯科耶烏斯季耶區|卡姆斯科耶烏斯季耶區]]{{en-link|休克耶沃|Syukeyevo}}处沉没，<ref name="ria death toll">{{cite web | url=http://en.beta.rian.ru/russia/20110711/165136343.html | title=Death toll in Volga boat tragedy reaches 54, over 50 missing | publisher=RIA Novosti | date=11 July 2011 | accessdate=11 July 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/606ZEPopZ?url=http://en.beta.rian.ru/russia/20110711/165136343.html | archivedate=2011-07-11 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>当时船上共有208人，<ref name="bbc2">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14103749 | title=Russia Volga boat tragedy: Medvedev orders review | publisher=BBC News Online | date=11 July 2011 | accessdate=11 July 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/606Y9Hs0J?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14103749 | archivedate=2011-07-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>正在从[[博爾加爾|博爾加爾]]驶往鞑靼斯坦共和国首都[[喀山|喀山]]。<ref name="bbc1">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14099637 | title=Russia fears 110 dead as boat sinks on Volga River | publisher=BBC News Online | date=11 July 2011 | accessdate=11 July 2011 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/606Y4BTtU?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-14099637 | archivedate=2011-07-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>这次灾难导致至少122人死亡。<ref name="svodboda122">{{cite web|url=https://www.svoboda.org/a/24275528.html|title="Булгария": все погибшие найдены|website=Радио Свобода|access-date=2021-06-05|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605030340/https://www.svoboda.org/a/24275528.html}}</ref>

“保加利亚号”的沉没是[[俄罗斯联邦|俄罗斯联邦]]最惨重的一次非军用船舶事故。包括前苏联民用船难事故在内，上一次最惨重的人员伤亡事故发生在1986年，当时“纳希莫夫上将号”撞入一艘货轮，导致423人死亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://top.rbc.ru/special/11/07/2011/604851.shtml |title=Крупнейшие катастрофы кораблей стран бывшего СССР :: Чрезвычайные происшествия :: Top.rbc.ru<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2011-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713221022/http://top.rbc.ru/special/11/07/2011/604851.shtml |archive-date=2011-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

